description:
Vernel Sensitive Skin Fabric Softener 33.81 oz (1L)

A Henkel Product

Vernel concentrated fabric softener helps protect colors and fibers while providing a fabulously fresh fragrance and even makes ironing easier. For everyone's protection it has been dermatologically tested for skin compatibility and is formulated to be environmentally friendly.

Type of product: Premium concentrated liquid fabric softener.

Application:
Vernel is added to the final rinse in the washing machine or washbasin. Vernel is suitable for washable fabrics made from natural, synthetic fibers or their blends.

Consumer benefits:
The cationic surfactants of Vernel help to protect the laundry fibers. Vernel gives the laundry a particularly soft and smooth handle. The nice fragrances give the rinsed laundry a pleasantly fresh odor. Vernel Sensitive Skin has the excellent skin compatibility and has been dermatologically tested.

Additional Information:
All Henkel products are environmentally friendly and “Septic Safe”.
